{
  "id": "354",
  "title": "新年的投票",
  "type": "answer_submission",
  "sections": [
    {
      "title": "",
      "content": "\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e这是一道\u003cdel\u003e送分\u003c/del\u003e提交答案题。\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e在打败了AlphaGo之后，SingleDog们决定选出一个新的狗群首领，建立起崭新的战后秩序。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e但是他们在研究了美国大选Trump的先例之后，发现每个独立的选民能获取的信息都是有限的，他们很好奇，这种情况下，选民还能不能选出正确的选择呢？\u003c/p\u003e",
      "misc": ""
    },
    {
      "title": "任务一",
      "content": "\u003cp\u003e我们把选举的过程抽象成以下的模型：\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MathJax_Preview\" style=\"color: inherit;\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-math\" id=\"MJXp-Span-1\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mi MJXp-italic\" id=\"MJXp-Span-2\"\u003en\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mo\" id=\"MJXp-Span-3\" style=\"margin-left: 0.333em; margin-right: 0.333em;\"\u003e=\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mn\" id=\"MJXp-Span-4\"\u003e15\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cscript type=\"math/tex\" id=\"MathJax-Element-1\"\u003en = 15\u003c/script\u003e 个选民围成一圈，每个人额头上有一个数字 \u003cspan class=\"MathJax_Preview\" style=\"color: inherit;\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-math\" id=\"MJXp-Span-5\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mn\" id=\"MJXp-Span-6\"\u003e0\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cscript type=\"math/tex\" id=\"MathJax-Element-2\"\u003e0\u003c/script\u003e 或者 \u003cspan class=\"MathJax_Preview\" style=\"color: inherit;\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-math\" id=\"MJXp-Span-7\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mn\" id=\"MJXp-Span-8\"\u003e1\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cscript type=\"math/tex\" id=\"MathJax-Element-3\"\u003e1\u003c/script\u003e，自己看不见自己额头上的数字，但是可以看见所有其他人头上的数字。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e每个人投一票给 \u003cspan class=\"MathJax_Preview\" style=\"color: inherit;\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-math\" id=\"MJXp-Span-9\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mn\" id=\"MJXp-Span-10\"\u003e0\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cscript type=\"math/tex\" id=\"MathJax-Element-4\"\u003e0\u003c/script\u003e 或者 \u003cspan class=\"MathJax_Preview\" style=\"color: inherit;\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-math\" id=\"MJXp-Span-11\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mn\" id=\"MJXp-Span-12\"\u003e1\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cscript type=\"math/tex\" id=\"MathJax-Element-5\"\u003e1\u003c/script\u003e，目标是要投出所有人额头上数字的异或和的正确值，最终投票的结果就是票数最多的一个。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e请你为每个人选择一个策略，在所有 \u003cspan class=\"MathJax_Preview\" style=\"color: inherit;\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-math\" id=\"MJXp-Span-13\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-msubsup\" id=\"MJXp-Span-14\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mn\" id=\"MJXp-Span-15\" style=\"margin-right: 0.05em;\"\u003e2\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mi MJXp-italic MJXp-script\" id=\"MJXp-Span-16\" style=\"vertical-align: 0.5em;\"\u003en\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mo\" id=\"MJXp-Span-17\" style=\"margin-left: 0.333em; margin-right: 0.333em;\"\u003e=\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mn\" id=\"MJXp-Span-18\"\u003e32768\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cscript type=\"math/tex\" id=\"MathJax-Element-6\"\u003e2^n = 32768\u003c/script\u003e 的可能的情况中，使得严格小于 \u003cspan class=\"MathJax_Preview\" style=\"color: inherit;\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-math\" id=\"MJXp-Span-19\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mn\" id=\"MJXp-Span-20\"\u003e7000\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cscript type=\"math/tex\" id=\"MathJax-Element-7\"\u003e7000\u003c/script\u003e 个情况投票结果无法投出正确值。\u003c/p\u003e",
      "misc": ""
    },
    {
      "title": "任务二",
      "content": "\u003cp\u003e在研究了任务一之后，狗群决定加大难度。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e在任务一的模型中，请你为每个人选择一个策略，使得在所有 \u003cspan class=\"MathJax_Preview\" style=\"color: inherit;\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-math\" id=\"MJXp-Span-21\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-msubsup\" id=\"MJXp-Span-22\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mn\" id=\"MJXp-Span-23\" style=\"margin-right: 0.05em;\"\u003e2\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mi MJXp-italic MJXp-script\" id=\"MJXp-Span-24\" style=\"vertical-align: 0.5em;\"\u003en\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mo\" id=\"MJXp-Span-25\" style=\"margin-left: 0.333em; margin-right: 0.333em;\"\u003e=\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mn\" id=\"MJXp-Span-26\"\u003e32768\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cscript type=\"math/tex\" id=\"MathJax-Element-8\"\u003e2^n = 32768\u003c/script\u003e 的可能的情况中，只有严格小于 \u003cspan class=\"MathJax_Preview\" style=\"color: inherit;\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-math\" id=\"MJXp-Span-27\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mn\" id=\"MJXp-Span-28\"\u003e2100\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cscript type=\"math/tex\" id=\"MathJax-Element-9\"\u003e2100\u003c/script\u003e 个情况投票结果无法投出正确值。\u003c/p\u003e",
      "misc": ""
    },
    {
      "title": "任务三",
      "content": "\u003cp\u003eSingleDog们对于这个正确率还是很不满意，他们认为，如果每个选民可以投任意 \u003cspan class=\"MathJax_Preview\" style=\"color: inherit;\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-math\" id=\"MJXp-Span-29\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mi MJXp-italic\" id=\"MJXp-Span-30\"\u003ex\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cscript type=\"math/tex\" id=\"MathJax-Element-10\"\u003ex\u003c/script\u003e 票（\u003cspan class=\"MathJax_Preview\" style=\"color: inherit;\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-math\" id=\"MJXp-Span-31\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mn\" id=\"MJXp-Span-32\"\u003e0\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mo\" id=\"MJXp-Span-33\" style=\"margin-left: 0.333em; margin-right: 0.333em;\"\u003e≤\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mi MJXp-italic\" id=\"MJXp-Span-34\"\u003ex\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mo\" id=\"MJXp-Span-35\" style=\"margin-left: 0.333em; margin-right: 0.333em;\"\u003e≤\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-msubsup\" id=\"MJXp-Span-36\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mn\" id=\"MJXp-Span-37\" style=\"margin-right: 0.05em;\"\u003e10\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mn MJXp-script\" id=\"MJXp-Span-38\" style=\"vertical-align: 0.5em;\"\u003e8\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cscript type=\"math/tex\" id=\"MathJax-Element-11\"\u003e0 \\leq x \\leq 10^8\u003c/script\u003e）来表示他们支持的情感的强烈程度，那么情况就会有所好转。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e那么如果把任务一的模型中每人只能投一票，改为每人可以投任意 \u003cspan class=\"MathJax_Preview\" style=\"color: inherit;\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-math\" id=\"MJXp-Span-39\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mn\" id=\"MJXp-Span-40\"\u003e0\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mo\" id=\"MJXp-Span-41\" style=\"margin-left: 0.333em; margin-right: 0.333em;\"\u003e≤\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mi MJXp-italic\" id=\"MJXp-Span-42\"\u003ex\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mo\" id=\"MJXp-Span-43\" style=\"margin-left: 0.333em; margin-right: 0.333em;\"\u003e≤\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-msubsup\" id=\"MJXp-Span-44\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mn\" id=\"MJXp-Span-45\" style=\"margin-right: 0.05em;\"\u003e10\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mn MJXp-script\" id=\"MJXp-Span-46\" style=\"vertical-align: 0.5em;\"\u003e8\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cscript type=\"math/tex\" id=\"MathJax-Element-12\"\u003e0 \\leq x \\leq 10^8\u003c/script\u003e 票呢？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e请留意这个任务中每人可以投任意 \u003cspan class=\"MathJax_Preview\" style=\"color: inherit;\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-math\" id=\"MJXp-Span-47\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mn\" id=\"MJXp-Span-48\"\u003e0\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mo\" id=\"MJXp-Span-49\" style=\"margin-left: 0.333em; margin-right: 0.333em;\"\u003e≤\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mi MJXp-italic\" id=\"MJXp-Span-50\"\u003ex\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mo\" id=\"MJXp-Span-51\" style=\"margin-left: 0.333em; margin-right: 0.333em;\"\u003e≤\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-msubsup\" id=\"MJXp-Span-52\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mn\" id=\"MJXp-Span-53\" style=\"margin-right: 0.05em;\"\u003e10\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mn MJXp-script\" id=\"MJXp-Span-54\" style=\"vertical-align: 0.5em;\"\u003e8\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cscript type=\"math/tex\" id=\"MathJax-Element-13\"\u003e0 \\leq x \\leq 10^8\u003c/script\u003e 票。\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e你能使只有严格小于 \u003cspan class=\"MathJax_Preview\" style=\"color: inherit;\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-math\" id=\"MJXp-Span-55\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mn\" id=\"MJXp-Span-56\"\u003e3\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cscript type=\"math/tex\" id=\"MathJax-Element-14\"\u003e3\u003c/script\u003e 个情况投票结果无法投出正确值吗？（平票的情况算做错误）\u003c/p\u003e",
      "misc": ""
    },
    {
      "title": "任务四",
      "content": "\u003cp\u003e但是理想模型和狗群现实还是有很大的差距，往往选民获取的信息只有一半甚至更少。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e现在 \u003cspan class=\"MathJax_Preview\" style=\"color: inherit;\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-math\" id=\"MJXp-Span-57\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mi MJXp-italic\" id=\"MJXp-Span-58\"\u003eC\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mo\" id=\"MJXp-Span-59\" style=\"margin-left: 0em; margin-right: 0em;\"\u003e(\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mi MJXp-italic\" id=\"MJXp-Span-60\"\u003en\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mo\" id=\"MJXp-Span-61\" style=\"margin-left: 0em; margin-right: 0.222em;\"\u003e,\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mi MJXp-italic\" id=\"MJXp-Span-62\"\u003ek\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mo\" id=\"MJXp-Span-63\" style=\"margin-left: 0em; margin-right: 0em;\"\u003e)\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cscript type=\"math/tex\" id=\"MathJax-Element-15\"\u003eC(n, k)\u003c/script\u003e 个人围成一圈，圈里是一个长度为 \u003cspan class=\"MathJax_Preview\" style=\"color: inherit;\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-math\" id=\"MJXp-Span-64\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mi MJXp-italic\" id=\"MJXp-Span-65\"\u003en\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mo\" id=\"MJXp-Span-66\" style=\"margin-left: 0.333em; margin-right: 0.333em;\"\u003e=\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mn\" id=\"MJXp-Span-67\"\u003e12\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cscript type=\"math/tex\" id=\"MathJax-Element-16\"\u003en = 12\u003c/script\u003e 的01串，每个人可以看到自己编号对应的一个大小为 \u003cspan class=\"MathJax_Preview\" style=\"color: inherit;\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-math\" id=\"MJXp-Span-68\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mi MJXp-italic\" id=\"MJXp-Span-69\"\u003ek\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mo\" id=\"MJXp-Span-70\" style=\"margin-left: 0.333em; margin-right: 0.333em;\"\u003e=\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mn\" id=\"MJXp-Span-71\"\u003e7\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cscript type=\"math/tex\" id=\"MathJax-Element-17\"\u003ek = 7\u003c/script\u003e 的位的集合（假设一个人可以看到的集合是 \u003cspan class=\"MathJax_Preview\" style=\"color: inherit;\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-math\" id=\"MJXp-Span-72\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mi MJXp-italic\" id=\"MJXp-Span-73\"\u003eS\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cscript type=\"math/tex\" id=\"MathJax-Element-18\"\u003eS\u003c/script\u003e，那么我们定义 \u003cspan class=\"MathJax_Preview\" style=\"color: inherit;\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-math\" id=\"MJXp-Span-74\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mi MJXp-italic\" id=\"MJXp-Span-75\"\u003ef\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mo\" id=\"MJXp-Span-76\" style=\"margin-left: 0em; margin-right: 0em;\"\u003e(\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mi MJXp-italic\" id=\"MJXp-Span-77\"\u003eS\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mo\" id=\"MJXp-Span-78\" style=\"margin-left: 0em; margin-right: 0em;\"\u003e)\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mo\" id=\"MJXp-Span-79\" style=\"margin-left: 0.333em; margin-right: 0.333em;\"\u003e=\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-msubsup\" id=\"MJXp-Span-80\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mo\" id=\"MJXp-Span-81\" style=\"margin-left: 0.111em; margin-right: 0.05em;\"\u003e∑\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mrow MJXp-script\" id=\"MJXp-Span-82\" style=\"vertical-align: -0.4em;\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mi MJXp-italic\" id=\"MJXp-Span-83\"\u003ex\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mo\" id=\"MJXp-Span-84\"\u003e∈\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mi MJXp-italic\" id=\"MJXp-Span-85\"\u003eS\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-msubsup\" id=\"MJXp-Span-86\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mn\" id=\"MJXp-Span-87\" style=\"margin-right: 0.05em;\"\u003e2\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mrow MJXp-script\" id=\"MJXp-Span-88\" style=\"vertical-align: 0.5em;\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mi MJXp-italic\" id=\"MJXp-Span-89\"\u003ex\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mo\" id=\"MJXp-Span-90\"\u003e−\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mn\" id=\"MJXp-Span-91\"\u003e1\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cscript type=\"math/tex\" id=\"MathJax-Element-19\"\u003ef(S)=\\sum_{x \\in S} 2^{x-1}\u003c/script\u003e，第 \u003cspan class=\"MathJax_Preview\" style=\"color: inherit;\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-math\" id=\"MJXp-Span-92\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mi MJXp-italic\" id=\"MJXp-Span-93\"\u003ei\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cscript type=\"math/tex\" id=\"MathJax-Element-20\"\u003ei\u003c/script\u003e 个人就是 \u003cspan class=\"MathJax_Preview\" style=\"color: inherit;\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-math\" id=\"MJXp-Span-94\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mi MJXp-italic\" id=\"MJXp-Span-95\"\u003ef\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mo\" id=\"MJXp-Span-96\" style=\"margin-left: 0em; margin-right: 0em;\"\u003e(\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mi MJXp-italic\" id=\"MJXp-Span-97\"\u003eS\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mo\" id=\"MJXp-Span-98\" style=\"margin-left: 0em; margin-right: 0em;\"\u003e)\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cscript type=\"math/tex\" id=\"MathJax-Element-21\"\u003ef(S)\u003c/script\u003e 第 \u003cspan class=\"MathJax_Preview\" style=\"color: inherit;\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-math\" id=\"MJXp-Span-99\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mi MJXp-italic\" id=\"MJXp-Span-100\"\u003ei\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cscript type=\"math/tex\" id=\"MathJax-Element-22\"\u003ei\u003c/script\u003e 小的人）。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e他们的目标是要选出对应的01串的每一位异或起来是 \u003cspan class=\"MathJax_Preview\" style=\"color: inherit;\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-math\" id=\"MJXp-Span-101\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mn\" id=\"MJXp-Span-102\"\u003e0\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cscript type=\"math/tex\" id=\"MathJax-Element-23\"\u003e0\u003c/script\u003e 还是 \u003cspan class=\"MathJax_Preview\" style=\"color: inherit;\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-math\" id=\"MJXp-Span-103\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mn\" id=\"MJXp-Span-104\"\u003e1\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cscript type=\"math/tex\" id=\"MathJax-Element-24\"\u003e1\u003c/script\u003e，现在每个人可以投任意 \u003cspan class=\"MathJax_Preview\" style=\"color: inherit;\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-math\" id=\"MJXp-Span-105\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mi MJXp-italic\" id=\"MJXp-Span-106\"\u003ex\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cscript type=\"math/tex\" id=\"MathJax-Element-25\"\u003ex\u003c/script\u003e 票（\u003cspan class=\"MathJax_Preview\" style=\"color: inherit;\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-math\" id=\"MJXp-Span-107\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mn\" id=\"MJXp-Span-108\"\u003e0\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mo\" id=\"MJXp-Span-109\" style=\"margin-left: 0.333em; margin-right: 0.333em;\"\u003e≤\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mi MJXp-italic\" id=\"MJXp-Span-110\"\u003ex\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mo\" id=\"MJXp-Span-111\" style=\"margin-left: 0.333em; margin-right: 0.333em;\"\u003e≤\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-msubsup\" id=\"MJXp-Span-112\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mn\" id=\"MJXp-Span-113\" style=\"margin-right: 0.05em;\"\u003e10\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mn MJXp-script\" id=\"MJXp-Span-114\" style=\"vertical-align: 0.5em;\"\u003e8\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cscript type=\"math/tex\" id=\"MathJax-Element-26\"\u003e0 \\leq x \\leq 10^8\u003c/script\u003e）。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e你能保证在全部 \u003cspan class=\"MathJax_Preview\" style=\"color: inherit;\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-math\" id=\"MJXp-Span-115\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-msubsup\" id=\"MJXp-Span-116\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mn\" id=\"MJXp-Span-117\" style=\"margin-right: 0.05em;\"\u003e2\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mrow MJXp-script\" id=\"MJXp-Span-118\" style=\"vertical-align: 0.5em;\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mn\" id=\"MJXp-Span-119\"\u003e12\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mo\" id=\"MJXp-Span-120\" style=\"margin-left: 0.333em; margin-right: 0.333em;\"\u003e=\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mn\" id=\"MJXp-Span-121\"\u003e4096\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cscript type=\"math/tex\" id=\"MathJax-Element-27\"\u003e2^{12} = 4096\u003c/script\u003e 种可能中，只有严格少于 \u003cspan class=\"MathJax_Preview\" style=\"color: inherit;\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-math\" id=\"MJXp-Span-122\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"MJXp-mn\" id=\"MJXp-Span-123\"\u003e80\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cscript type=\"math/tex\" id=\"MathJax-Element-28\"\u003e80\u003c/script\u003e 种无法选出正确的异或和吗？（平票的情况算做错误）\u003c/p\u003e",
